short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly access your most-visited LinkedIn profiles. Skip LinkedIn's slow search bar and search right in the extension!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Skip LinkedIn's search bar and pull up your LinkedIn contacts faster using this Chrome extension.

LinkedIn Searchbar saves each profile you view and makes them accessible for quick searching and access.

Access the extension with the "Ctrl+." shortcut ("Cmd+." for macOS) and start searching!

Free and open source!
https://github.com/awei82/linkedin-recents
